        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You tap on a chip of mica and say a word of power, the tiny vibrations in the stone replicated at many times the strength at a location you choose, blasting your foes with a painfully intense ringing noise and an eruption of force.</em></p><p><strong>Constitution Save</strong> </p><p>&amp;reference[Construct]{Constructs} have disadvantage on this saving throw.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Targets take [[/damage 3d8 thunder]] damage.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d8 thunder]]{1d8} for each spell level above 2nd.</p>",
